::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe suddenly stops in the forest, his scanners picking up a Maximal 
nearby. He smiles to himself. Killing someone would help his mood.....

Silently transforming, DeathScythe takes out his pistol, silently heading for 
the signature (Lunarpine).
